  • Packages that use SimpleRecord 
    Package Description
    com.koverse.sdk.data
    Contains components related to Koverse Records and the values in them.
    com.koverse.sdk.export
    Components related to exporting data sets as files.
    com.koverse.sdk.ingest.records
    Components related to importing records.
    com.koverse.sdk.record
    Contains JDBC related components for records.
    com.koverse.sdk.record.transform
    Contains components on transforming records.
    com.koverse.sdk.record.webapp
    Koverse can be extended to enable downoading of data set records as any type of file.
    com.koverse.sdk.sink
    Contains components for exporting records.
    com.koverse.sdk.sink.database
    Database Sink support.
    com.koverse.sdk.source
    Components for importing data.
    com.koverse.sdk.sql.convert
    Contains internal use components for converting records to and from SQL types.
    com.koverse.sdk.test
    Test harness classes for running and testing sources, transforms, and sinks.
    com.koverse.sdk.test.spark  
    com.koverse.sdk.transform
    Transform-related API.
    com.koverse.sdk.transform.java  
    com.koverse.sdk.transform.scala  
    com.koverse.sdk.transform.spark  
    com.koverse.sdk.transform.spark.sql
    Spark SQL based transforms.
    com.koverse.sdk.transform.spark.sql.row
    Internal use components for converting records to and from Spark SQL table rows.
    com.koverse.sdk.util
    Components in this package are intended for internal use.
